Install Java 17
Clone the Git repo to the local
Git Repo -> 
Right Click on the project and Downloaded Maven Sources
Run the TestRunner File (src -> test -> testrunner -> TestRunner)
Reports are generated in target folder (cucumber-reports.html) -> right click on reports and open in browser

Feature Files ->
crispySuccotash.feature file contains the signup and login testcases

Step Definitions ->
Hooks : contains the code which has be  executed before each scenario
signupandloginStepDefinition : contains the steps of the testcases

Pages ->
SignupandLoginPage : contains the test logic code

Utils ->
CommonContent : contains the error message text
PlaywrightManager : contains the playwright code to open the browser



